snippet: Boston Public Library officials said Thursday that two rare and valuable artworks that vanished last month have been found, and they never left the library.
abstract: Boston Public Library reports that it has located Rembrandt etching and Durer engraving that vanished in May; rare and valuable artworks were located within building.
lead_paragraph: Boston Public Library officials said Thursday that two rare and valuable artworks that vanished last month have been found, and they never left the library.

headline.main: Massachusetts: Art Lost and Found in Library
headline.print_headline: Massachusetts: Art Lost and Found in Library
